      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;Called Dave after our heater started smoking back into the room. He diagnosed a blocked flue and cleaned the full system. Quick, professional, no mess. Will be booking every year from now on.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Kylie M., Pakenham</p></div>
      <div class="review-card"><div class="review-stars">&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;&#9733;</div><p class="review-text">&ldquo;New estate home but the heater had been in for eight years without a professional service. David cleaned the flue and pointed out some baffle deterioration worth keeping an eye on. Great service at a fair price.&rdquo;</p><p class="review-author">Andrew C., Pakenham</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

